content:
[[div class="scp-image-block block-center" style="width:100%;"]]
[[image http://kaktuskontainer.wdfiles.com/local--files/the-hanged-king-s-comedy/Courtyard style="width:100%;" link=#]]
[[div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:100%;"]]
//国王的宫殿中，那医者正在等候。//    插画提供自[[*user Dex V]]
[[/div]]
[[/div]]

[[div class="main-body-div"]]


++ **__缢王谐调__**


> [[span class="ruby"]]酷刑无尽，应允莫赎，[[span class="rt"]]The spiteful's torment shall permit [[/span]][[/span]]
> [[span class="ruby"]]极权黑幕，裂世而出。[[span class="rt"]]Glom of power whence the worlds split.[[/span]][[/span]] 
> 
> [[span class="ruby"]]黑星长恨，永无止境，[[span class="rt"]]And black stars hate without relent;[[/span]][[/span]]  
> [[span class="ruby"]][[[a-wandsman-in-the-court-of-the-hanged-king|君王]]]恶戏，戛然而停。[[span class="rt"]]The King's pernicious game is spent.[[/span]][[/span]] 
> 
> [[span class="ruby"]]篡夺王位，败绩无数，[[span class="rt"]]Failed usurper ten trillion times, [[/span]][[/span]] 
> [[span class="ruby"]]双子无罪，降罪以促。[[span class="rt"]]Fueled by those two who sinned no crimes. [[/span]][[/span]] 
> 
> [[span class="ruby"]]君临天下，自此而始，[[span class="rt"]]So now my reign stands to begin,[[/span]][[/span]]  
> [[span class="ruby"]]苦闷之庭，罪戕不止。[[span class="rt"]]Anguish, the court of strife and sin. [[/span]][[/span]] 
> 
> [[span class="ruby"]]碌碌万民，尽在手中，[[span class="rt"]]Existence within my control, [[/span]][[/span]]
> [[span class="ruby"]]幽幽魂灵，皆在苦中。[[span class="rt"]]Agony wracking every soul. [[/span]][[/span]]
> 
> [[span class="ruby"]]王拥大罪，罪为王饲。[[span class="rt"]]Thus, I will feed the king his sin, [[/span]][[/span]] 
> [[span class="ruby"]]如此至死，死无可死。[[span class="rt"]]To die 'till he can't die again! [[/span]][[/span]] 
> 
> [[span class="ruby"]] 尘埃落定，王座归吾，[[span class="rt"]]Thereafter I will take my throne,[[/span]][[/span]] 
> [[span class="ruby"]]血肉条条，剥离白骨。[[span class="rt"]]All flesh having been stripped to bone. [[/span]][[/span]]
> [[span class="ruby"]]众生皆卒，苦王所执，[[span class="rt"]]All lives are pawns of the Anguished King's [[/span]][[/span]] 
> [[span class="ruby"]]系于傀线，惨虐致死。[[span class="rt"]]To suffer and die on my puppet-strings. [[/span]][[/span]] 
[[/div]]
-----

[[div class="main-body-div-r"]]
[[=]]
++ **__到目前为止的故事……__**
[[/=]]

> //“那些抛却了死亡的命运和战胜巨大怖灵的人的谣言充斥了Rydell的思绪。最后，在缢王的宫廷内，他将有第二次机会来揭开这些秘密的真相。”//
> - [[size 80%]]**[[[http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/of-doctors-and-alagadda|医生与阿拉卡达]]]** 由[[*user Gabriel Jade]]和[[*user Blacknife09]]写就[[/size]]
----
> //“他读了多少次那本书？而我在这儿多久了，以至于忘记了一切？他说不出他在楼梯上坐了多久，一件可怜的、难以言说的事。当听到背后传来骨掌踏踏声时，他终于转过身来。”//
> - [[size 80%]]**[[[http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/pestilence-in-the-court-of-the-hanged-king|缢王宫廷中的瘟疫]]]** 由[[*user Gabriel Jade]]写就[[/size]]
----
> //“混乱、痛苦的哭声和尖叫声在走廊里回荡；为痛苦之主谱就一首交响曲。瑟瑟作抖，如午夜般湿润而血红，绝望的是，它仍没有死亡。它饱受折磨，心神无宁，心知它已孤立无援。//
> 
> //然而这并非真实。”//
> - [[size 80%]]**[[[http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/in-the-shadow-of-the-anguished-lord|痛苦尊主的阴影之下]]]** 由[[*user Gabriel Jade]]写就[[/size]]
----
> //“……再说一次，0-3-5拥有一个可能对[数据已丢失]分泌物免疫的实体。大多数武力小组都[数据已丢失] 听了几分钟它的声音。我们遭到了猛烈的炮火袭击。他妈的都要怪他们，他们让我们躲在这里。[数据已丢失]…个机会可用于赶上warh… [剩余数据已丢失]"//
> - [[size 80%]]**[[[http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/everyone-wears-a-mask|每个人都戴着面具]]]** 由[[*user Gabriel Jade]]写就[[/size]]
----
> //星光在第五个夜晚闪耀。众星可以看到那朵黑云。那位医者，他已再无未完的事业，离开了与世隔绝的破败木制教堂。//
>  - [[size 80%]]**[[[An Angel who has Forsaken Sympathy|一位抛弃了同情的天使]]]** 由[[*user Gabriel Jade]]写就[[/size]]
----
> //一个男人和一位医者站在黑暗的走廊中。//
>  - [[size 80%]]**[[[Do No Harm|莫伤害]]]** by [[*user Gabriel Jade]]和[[*user Doctor Cimmerian]][[/size]]
[[/div]]
[[>]]
++ **每个人都戴着面具。**
[[/>]]


[[module CSS]]

a:visited {
color: #BC4123;
}

#main-content {
    background-color: #ffffca;
}

@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Playfair+Display:400,700,900,400italic,700italic,900italic');
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Droid+Serif:400,700,400italic,700italic');
h1, #page-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    color: black;
    padding: 0 0 0.25em;
    margin: 0 0 0.6em;
    font-weight: normal;
}
h1 {
    margin-top: 0.7em;
    padding: 0;
    font-weight: bold;
}
h2, h3, h4, h6, h7 {
    margin: 0.5em 0 0.4em;
    padding: 0;
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    color: black;
    font-style: italic;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-shadow: 1px 1px 1px #000000;
    text-shadow: 1px 1px 1px rgba(0,0,0,.8);
}
h5 {
   margin: 0.5em 0 0.4em;
    padding: 0;
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    color: black;
    font-style: italic;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
}
#page-title {
    border-color: black;
}

.head-box-2{
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    padding: 10px 15px 10px 15px;
    width: 89%;
    position: relative;
    text-align: left;
    line-height: 20px;
    display: inline-block;
    margin: 0 25px 20px -360px;
    background-color: #fdf5e8;
    border-radius: 8px 8px 8px 8px;
    font-size: 1.5em;
}

.head-box{
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    padding: 10px 15px 10px 15px;
    width: 89%;
    position: relative;
    border: 3px double #BC4123;
    text-align: left;
    line-height: 20px;
    display: inline-block;
    margin: 0 25px 20px -360px;
    border-radius: 8px 8px 8px 8px;
    background-color: #fdf5e8;

}


.head{
    text-align: right;
    position: relative;
}

.main-body-div{
    font-family: 'Droid Serif', serif;
    font-size: 1.5em;
    line-height: 20px;
    width: 89%;
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0 1% 0 1%;
    vertical-align: top;
    margin-bottom: 25px;
    transition: all .7s;
    border-left: 3px double #BC4123;
    border-top: 3px double #BC4123;
}

blockquote {
    background-color:  #fdf5e8;
    color: black;
    font-family: 'Droid Serif', serif;
    list-style: none;
}
.main-body-div-r{
    font-family: 'Droid Serif', serif;
    font-size: 1.5em;
    line-height: 20px;
    width: 89%;
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0 1% 0 1%;
    vertical-align: top;
    margin-bottom: 25px;
    transition: all .7s;
    border-right: 4px double #BC4123;
    border-bottom:  3px double #BC4123;

}
}

#header h1 a {
    font-family: "comic sans mf", times, serif;
    content: "王庭之上";
}

#header h1 a::before {
    font-family: "comic sans mf", times, serif;
    content: "王庭之上";
}

#header h1 a span{
    display: block;
    content: "";
    visibility: hidden;
}

#header h2 span {
    display: block;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 19px 0;
    line-height: 0px;
    max-height: 0px;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: transparent;
    text-shadow: none;
}

#header h2 span::before {
    content: "人人覆面";
    display: block;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0px 0;
    line-height: 0px;
    max-height: 0px;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #ffffff;
    text-shadow: 1px 1px 1px #000;
    text-shadow: 1px 1px 1px rgba(0,0,0,.8);
}
[[/module]]
